        <div class="contentHeading">Downloads</div>

        <p>The current version is Alpha build <span id="buildNumber">XX</span>.</p>
		<br />
        <p><b>Tawala requires</b> that the following be installed on your computer:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><b>Windows 2000 or Windows XP</b> (Professional or Home Edition). You should also have the most
                recent Windows updates for your operating system.</li>
            <li><b>Microsoft .NET Framework Version 2.0</b>. If you do not already have the .NET 2.0
                Framework on your system, it will be installed as part of the Tawala installation.
                <br /><br />
            	<em>.Net is about 22MB. This may take a long time to download depending on your
            	connection speed.</em>
            	<br /><br />
            </li>
            <li>A <b>broadband connection</b> to the Internet.</li>
            <li>An email client application (e.g. Outlook, Outlook Express, Mozilla Thunderbird).</li>
        </ul>

		<br />
        <p>Ready to go? </p>
